'''Tamasiḥit''' d [[ajjed]] ideg ttamnen medden belli [[Ṛebbi]] d yiwen, iṣubb ɣer medden s wedmaw n bunadem : [[Yeccu]] (Ɛisa). Imasiḥiyen ttamnen belli Ɛisa ur yesɛi ara baba-s : ilul ala seg yiwen n tmeṭṭut : [[Meryem]] s tezmert n Rebbi. Imasiḥiyen ttamnen bell Ɛisa d lmasiḥ iwmui ad yeslek [[Udayen]] u ad yexelq tamurt n Israyil tameqqrant, ɣas akken ur yexdim ara akk tiɣawsiwi-agi, nutni ttamnen belli a d-yuɣal tikkelt nniḍen akken a tt-yexdem. 

Imasiḥiyen umnen di Adlis Iqedsen neɣ [[Abenǧil]] neɣ [[Abenǧil|Inǧil]] , ayen isɛan [[turat|tira]] s [[taɛebrit|tɛebrit]] d [[Abenǧil|tira]] s [[tayunanit|tyunanit]]<!--, turat idlis n udayen, inğil d timucuha ɣef tudert n Ɛisa-->.

